# Listae theme security

- Never execute user-supplied JavaScript on profile pages or previews.
- HTML: allowlist only; strip scripts, event handlers, dangerous URLs.
- CSS `@import`: allow **only** `fonts.googleapis.com` and `fonts.gstatic.com`.
- Validation errors must cite **line/column** or the **exact** rejected `@import`/URL.
- Serve preview/public theme UI in iframe `sandbox` without `allow-scripts`.
- Follow skill `listae-theme-engine` and ADR `docs/decisions/005-profile-html-css.md`.
